graph LR
    TrainingOp[Kubeflow Training Operator<br/>v1.9.0]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    TrainingOp -->|container orchestration| K8s[Kubernetes 1.27+]
    TrainingOp -->|controller framework| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime v0.19+]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    TrainingOp -.->|gang scheduling| Volcano[Volcano Scheduler]
    TrainingOp -.->|gang scheduling alt| SchedulerPlugins[Scheduler Plugins]
    TrainingOp -.->|metrics collection| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator]
    TrainingOp -.->|traffic mgmt<br/>sidecar disabled| Istio[Istio Service Mesh]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    TrainingOp -->|UI integration| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
    TrainingOp -->|post-training storage| ModelRegistry[Model Registry]
    TrainingOp -.->|orchestration| DistributedWorkloads[Distributed Workloads]

    %% External Services
    TrainingOp -->|pull images| ContainerRegistry[Container Registry]
    TrainingOp -->|training data/models| ObjectStorage[S3/Object Storage]
    TrainingOp -->|API calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]

    %% Framework Support (What the operator enables)
    subgraph Frameworks["Supported ML Frameworks"]
        PyTorch[PyTorch<br/>Elastic Training]
        TensorFlow[TensorFlow<br/>Parameter Server]
        MPI[MPI<br/>HPC Workloads]
        XGBoost[XGBoost]
        PaddlePaddle[PaddlePaddle]
        JAX[JAX]
    end

    TrainingOp -.->|enables distributed| Frameworks

